annotationA: AT30951p; Unfolded protein binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: protein folding; 'de novo' protein folding; Belongs to the GroES chaperonin family
annotationB: GrpE protein homolog, mitochondrial; Essential component of the PAM complex, a complex required for the translocation of transit peptide-containing proteins from the inner membrane into the mitochondrial matrix in an ATP-dependent manner.
